---
layout: base.njk
title: Joseph Karl — Full-stack Developer
description: Portfolio of Joseph Karl, a full-stack developer who designs and ships reliable, thoughtful web products end-to-end.
---

<main id="main">
  <span id="top"></span>

  <!-- ============ HERO ============ -->
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="hero-meta">{% if site.available %}<span class="status"><span class="pulse" aria-hidden="true"></span> Available for new work</span>{% endif %}{% if site.available and site.resume %}, {% endif %}{% if site.resume %}<a class="resume-link" href="{{ site.resume | url }}" download>download my résumé <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">↓</span></a>{% endif %}</p>
      <h1>Full-stack developer building <span class="accent">reliable</span> web products.</h1>
      <p class="hero-lead">
        I'm Joseph — I design and ship end-to-end applications, from the data model
        up to the last pixel. I care about clarity, performance, and code that ages well.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#work">See selected work</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="#contact">Get in touch <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">→</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ WORK (the highlight) ============ -->
  <section class="section" id="work">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Selected work</p>
        <h2>A few things I've designed, built, and shipped.</h2>
        <p class="sub">Each project below is something I owned end-to-end — problem framing, architecture, and delivery.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="work-scroller reveal">
        <div class="work-controls">
          <span class="work-hint">Scroll to explore →</span>
          <button class="scroll-btn" type="button" data-scroll="prev" aria-label="Previous projects" disabled>
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M15 18l-6-6 6-6"/></svg>
          </button>
          <button class="scroll-btn" type="button" data-scroll="next" aria-label="More projects">
            <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M9 6l6 6-6 6"/></svg>
          </button>
        </div>

        <div class="work-track" tabindex="0" role="region" aria-label="Selected projects — horizontally scrollable">
          {% for project in projects %}
          <article class="work-slide">
            <p class="work-index" aria-hidden="true">{% if loop.index < 10 %}0{% endif %}{{ loop.index }}</p>
            <div class="project-visual" aria-hidden="true">{{ project.visual | safe }}</div>
            <div class="work-body">
              {% if project.liveUrl %}
              <h3><a class="stretched" href="{{ project.liveUrl }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><span class="title-text">{{ project.name }}</span></a></h3>
              {% else %}
              <h3>{{ project.name }}</h3>
              {% endif %}
              <div class="work-detail">
                <p>{{ project.blurb }}</p>
                <ul class="tags">{% for tag in project.tags %}<li>{{ tag }}</li>{% endfor %}</ul>
                {% if project.liveUrl %}
                <span class="project-link">Visit live site <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">↗</span></span>
                {% endif %}
              </div>
            </div>
          </article>
          {% endfor %}

          <!-- Trailing room so the last project can still scroll to the left edge -->
          <div class="work-spacer" aria-hidden="true"></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ WRITING ============ -->
  <section class="section" id="writing">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Writing</p>
        <h2>Articles &amp; publications.</h2>
        <p class="sub">Essays and deep-dives on building for the web — the ideas behind the work, written down.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="writing-shell reveal">
        <div class="writing-empty">
          <p class="writing-empty-title">Nothing published yet.</p>
          <p class="writing-empty-note">Essays and deep-dives are in the works — check back soon.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ CERTIFICATES ============ -->
  <section class="section" id="certificates">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Certifications</p>
        <h2>Credentials, kept compact.</h2>
        <p class="sub">A capped, scrollable list — it holds every certificate inside a fixed height instead of running away down the page.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="certs-shell reveal">
        <nav class="certs-tabs" aria-label="Jump to certificate category">
          {% for group in certificates.groups %}
          <button class="cert-tab" type="button" data-cert-tab="cert-group-{{ group.label | slug }}"{% if loop.first %} aria-current="true"{% endif %}>
            {{ group.label }} <span class="ct-count">{{ group.items | length }}</span>
          </button>
          {% endfor %}
        </nav>
        <div class="certs-scroll" tabindex="0" role="region" aria-label="Certifications — scrollable list">
          {% for group in certificates.groups %}
          <section class="cert-group" id="cert-group-{{ group.label | slug }}" aria-label="{{ group.label }} certifications">
            <ul class="certs-list">
              {% for cert in group.items %}
              <li class="cert">
                <div class="c-main">
                  <a class="c-name" href="{{ cert.file | url }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" title="{{ cert.name }} · {{ cert.issuer }} · {{ cert.date }}">{{ cert.name }}</a>
                  <span class="c-issuer">{{ cert.issuer }}</span>
                </div>
                <span class="c-year">{{ cert.year }}</span>
              </li>
              {% endfor %}
            </ul>
          </section>
          {% endfor %}
        </div>
        <p class="certs-note">{{ certificates.total }} certifications across {{ certificates.groups | length }} track{% if certificates.groups | length != 1 %}s{% endif %} · scroll within the panel to see them all.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ EXPERIENCE ============ -->
  <section class="section" id="experience">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Experience</p>
        <h2>Where I've spent my time.</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="timeline reveal">
        {% for job in experience %}
        <div class="timeline-item">
          <p class="when">{{ job.when }}</p>
          <h3>{{ job.role }}</h3>
          <p class="role-org">{{ job.org }}{% if job.meta %} · {{ job.meta }}{% endif %}</p>
          <p>{{ job.summary }}</p>
          {% if job.points %}
          <ul class="timeline-points">
            {% for point in job.points %}<li>{{ point }}</li>{% endfor %}
          </ul>
          {% endif %}
        </div>
        {% endfor %}
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ STACK ============ -->
  <section class="section" id="stack">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">Toolkit</p>
        <h2>The tools I reach for.</h2>
      </div>
      <dl class="stack-groups reveal">
        <div class="stack-group">
          <dt>Languages</dt>
          <dd><span>Ruby</span><span>TypeScript / JavaScript</span><span>Python</span><span>SQL</span></dd>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-group">
          <dt>Frameworks</dt>
          <dd><span>Rails 8</span><span>Hotwire</span><span>Node</span><span>Stimulus</span></dd>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-group">
          <dt>Data</dt>
          <dd><span>PostgreSQL</span><span>Solid Queue / Cache / Cable</span><span>SQLite</span></dd>
        </div>
        <div class="stack-group">
          <dt>Platform</dt>
          <dd><span>Docker</span><span>Kamal</span><span>AWS</span><span>Linux</span><span>CI/CD</span></dd>
        </div>
      </dl>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ ABOUT ============ -->
  <section class="section" id="about">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="section-head reveal">
        <p class="eyebrow">About</p>
      </div>
      <div class="about reveal">
        <p style="font-size:var(--step-h3); color:var(--ink); max-width:var(--measure);">
          I build software the way I'd want to use it — <strong>clear, fast, and honest</strong>
          about its edges.
        </p>
        <p style="margin-top:var(--space-6)">
          My work sits at the intersection of engineering and design. I like problems that
          need both a solid data model and a considered interface, and I care as much about
          the quiet details — empty states, loading, error copy — as the headline features.
        </p>
        <p>
          When I'm not building, I'm usually reading about systems design, refining my own
          tools, or exploring on foot.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- ============ CONTACT ============ -->
  <section class="contact" id="contact">
    <div class="container">
      <p class="eyebrow reveal">Contact</p>
      <div class="reveal">
        <h2 style="max-width:16ch; margin-top:var(--space-4)">Have something to build? Let's talk.</h2>
        <a class="big-mail" href="mailto:{{ site.email }}">{{ site.email }}</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</main>
